(26113, 'Omega 3 strem 1000 mg 20 capsules', 'اوميجا 3 ستريم 20 كبسولة', '115', '175', 'Fish oil', 'Unitrade pharma', 'Capsule', 'كبسولة', '', 'Support brain function', '1000 mg', 'Under FDA approval, fish oil pharmaceuticals are typically products consisting of a combination of the omega-3-fatty acids eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and are indicated primarily as an adjunct to diet to reduce triglyceride levels in adult patients with severe (>=500 mg/dL) hypertriglyceridemia [FDA Label, F36].
